data.value: Explain what you were doing that caused the bug. This will be posted publicly at https://github.com/StageBoxBrawl/StageBoxIssues/issues, so do not put any personal information here. It may be beneficial to you to sign your report with a username unless you wish to stay anonymous. It is also very helpful to report the issue on our Discord at https://discord.gg/s7c8763
